Sassaƙan duwatsu cikin Amirka ta Kudu na nuna hoton mutane na hawan halittun irin kamar da na Diplodocus kuma, abin mamaki, suna da sanannun surorin irin na Triceratops-, Pterodactyl- da Tryannosaurus Rex.
